Poland’s PBG Agrees to Buy 50% of Boiler Maker Rafako for $193.4 Million

-- B y   D a v i d   M c Q u a i d
-- 
2011-06-28T04:37:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/poland-s-pbg-agrees-to-buy-50-of-boiler-maker-rafako-for-193-4-million.html
PBG,  Poland ’s second-largest builder
by market value, late yesterday said it had signed a preliminary
agreement to purchase a 50 percent stake in industrial equipment
maker  Rafako SA (RFK)  for no more than 540.8 million zloty ($193.4
million).  PBG agreed to buy the majority stake in Rafako from a
Cyprus-based unit of Elektrim SA, subject to the approval of
Poland’s competition regulator.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David McQuaid at 
 dmcquaid1@bloomberg.net  